.page-header
  %h1
    GeoLocation Challenge
    =link_to "Main Page", root_path, class: "btn btn-success btn-xs"
    =link_to "All Locations", locations_path, class: "btn btn-success btn-xs"
.div.main
  .row
    .col-md-4.col-md-offset-1
      %h1.main-header About
  .row
    .col-md-6.col-md-offset-1.locations.well
      .div.about
        %h1 What is this?
        %h4
          This is application was created to have accept an incoming TSV file as an upload, parse the information and display it.
          On the main page you can find the closest five points to the specified location but also a table displaying all of the locations
          loaded from the TSV file and sorted by distance.
